item.title: the end (part 2) - 1
item.description: Hey. (keep scrolling down!) It's been a year... It's been a while, isn't it? who are you? It's me. Don't you recognize me? ... you... Yeah. You have died. One year ago. That was a painful and horrible death, I must admit. But to what end? A creative block? For I am your creator, and you are a figment of my imagination. I have complete control over this world and its destiny.
